summary: DibellaSeven is a custom body replacer somewhere between SevenBase, TBD, and a little something of UNPC.
descriptionHtml:
---------------------------------------------------------------
DibellaSeven by Crazy1918 and AmevenAstral9.
---------------------------------------------------------------
------------------
-Description:
------------------
"Dibella has blessed the women of Skyrim with a hardy but beautiful body to survive with style
in it's harsh lands"....The milkdrinker famous words.
Based on SevenBase Bombshell, Touched by dibella and a little something of UNPC, UNPCM and the great idea of a dear friend i made DibellaSeven a custom Body replacer.
First the idea was to combine the upper TBD body with the lower SevenBase body, of course i had to add some modifications.
I tried to make it look as realestic as possible, while remaining in SevenBase and TBD territory.
Weightslider and TBBP support.

---------------------
-Requirements:
---------------------
Same as SevenBase BombShell.

-----------------
-Installation:
-----------------
Install using NMM or any other mod manager.

--------------------
-Compatibility:
--------------------
Compatible with every UNP texture.

----------------------------
